text: Jardinópolis is a municipality in the state of São Paulo, Brazil, in the outskirts of Ribeirão Preto. The population is 44,970 (2020 est.) in an area of 502 km2.Instituto Brasileiro de Geografia e Estatística ==Location== It is located in the state of São Paulo in Brazil. São Paulo is in the southeast part of Brazil. Jardinópolis is about 205 miles (330 kilometers) away from the big city of São Paulo. ==References== Category:Municipalities in São Paulo (state)
title: Jardinópolis, São Paulo
